<br>
Never expect loot.<br>
<br>
If someone is nice enough to give you something that you need, consider it an act of generosity on their part, not the expected or required action.<br>
<br>
And if you win something in NBG, you should turn in the item you are replacing with the new item. Unless it's no drop it should go to others in the group. If you can't give it to them because it's not yours (Guild property, borrowing from a friend, etc), or you just don't want to, you should random on it with everyone else.<br>
<br>
I hate pickup groups.<br>
